Okay, real talk, my hair has been feeling a little lacklustre lately. 😩  Stress, heat styling, you name it, it’s taken a toll.  So, I’m super excited to be trying the new Dove Scalp + Hair Therapy range!  I’ve heard amazing things about their scalp serum, and the fact that it’s co-created with dermatologists gives me even more confidence.  It’s packed with ingredients like Zinc Peptide and Niacinamide, which are supposed to be amazing for scalp health and hair density.  I’m hoping to see some real improvement in the next few weeks.  Has anyone else tried this range?  Let me know your thoughts in the comments! 👇

Witnessing this elaborate hairstyle unwind is so satisfying.  My secret to healthy, strong hair that can handle these styles?  Consistent care! I also use a peptide repair shampoo on the lengths to keep them strong. These habits have seriously minimized hair fall, making even the most complex looks possible.
